intitule: Introduction to container orchestration with kubernetes
descriptif:
It is a great pleasure to invite you all to a talk entitled "Introduction to container orchestration with kubernetes" by Abdellfetah SGHIOUAR, Cloud Engineer at GOOGLE SWEDEN. The talk will take place at the Grand Amphitheatre of ENSIAS, Wednesday 27/11, at 4 pm.
Description of the talk:
Kubernetes is a powerful open-source system, initially developed by Google, for managing containerized applications in a clustered environment. It aims to provide better ways of managing related, distributed components and services across varied infrastructure.
In this talk weâ€™ll discuss some of Kubernetesâ€™ basic concepts. We will talk about the architecture of the system, the problems it solves, and the model that it uses to handle containerized deployments and scaling.
Bio of speaker:
Abdellfettah Sghiouar is a Google Cloud Engineer with a focus on Serveless, IoT, ML and Devops Methodologies. A big fan and supporter of OSS software and evangelising for Kubernetes.
